title: Sam Smith's 'Writing’s on the Wall' Music Video From 'Spectre' - Watch Now!
text: Sam Smith just debuted the brand new music video for the James Bond theme song “Writing’s on the Wall” from Spectre! The 23-year-old entertainer stars in the video, which also shows footage of the James Bond stars Daniel Craig and Monica Bellucci! PHOTOS: Check out the latest pics of Sam Smith The video was directed [...] »
